{"tid":2378460,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"買完野 覺得自己冇錢","createTime":"2021-01-24T13:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T01:12:33.000Z","uid":325392,"like":31,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e834b1ca9bb42c19389e94fdf39554bc3e6da6da","tid":2378460,"uid":325392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:08:25.000Z","msg":"有冇人好似我咁<br />\n買咗幾萬蚊既袋 過咗幾日覺得冇咗舊錢<br />\n好冇安全感<br />\n跟住好想拎去賣<br />\n但賣完之後 有錢喇<br />\n又好想買番<br />\n不停重複<br />\n究竟係咪有病"},{"pid":"8d674211ec37ed2cd6bc73110a69bbd65e443b9a","tid":2378460,"uid":177089,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:08:49.000Z","msg":"係 你有病"},{"pid":"7a512ecf04fbed7fe9d08c412d3711caa19231c4","tid":2378460,"uid":60042,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:12:14.000Z","msg":"你試下放幾萬蚊 現金係屋企 <br />\n<br />\n下次買野果陣 望住呢幾萬蚊唸下你要用幾耐時間先揾到呢d錢<br />\n<br />\n同埋買完個袋可以帶比你既開心又有幾長時間"},{"pid":"93b03f309c9f756deb81c6bcd5c9559b3df7eccf","tid":2378460,"uid":325392,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"7a512ecf04fbed7fe9d08c412d3711caa19231c4","tid":2378460,"uid":60042,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:12:14.000Z","msg":"你試下放幾萬蚊 現金係屋企 <br />\n<br />\n下次買野果陣 望住呢幾萬蚊唸下你要用幾耐時間先揾到呢d錢<br />\n<br />\n同埋買完個袋可以帶比你既開心又有幾長時間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"但望住幾萬現金又唔開心<br />\n但個袋見住又真係開心d"},{"pid":"b1eb809cfc0c212fd5ccf90e4c905d22afdd8400","tid":2378460,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:14:47.000Z","msg":"心理 生理都貧窮"},{"pid":"7bdd69bc441b7454ddaf5f124b8fc380e191a2e4","tid":2378460,"uid":382485,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:15:43.000Z","msg":"真係好想要<br />\n覺得自己會用好多次先買 咁樣起碼抵啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f828ba8862b406c9626a2c69caac7592a8d3057c","tid":2378460,"uid":60042,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"93b03f309c9f756deb81c6bcd5c9559b3df7eccf","tid":2378460,"uid":325392,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"7a512ecf04fbed7fe9d08c412d3711caa19231c4","tid":2378460,"uid":60042,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:12:14.000Z","msg":"你試下放幾萬蚊 現金係屋企 <br />\n<br />\n下次買野果陣 望住呢幾萬蚊唸下你要用幾耐時間先揾到呢d錢<br />\n<br />\n同埋買完個袋可以帶比你既開心又有幾長時間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"但望住幾萬現金又唔開心<br />\n但個袋見住又真係開心d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:17:23.000Z","msg":"甘你望住個袋會開心係正常<br />\n但呢你可以開心得幾耐<br />\n我自己黎講 一件唔係實用 經常會用既野帶比我開心最多都係得幾日<br />\n之後果樣野對我黎講真係可有可無<br />\n<br />\n當然如果個袋你一個星期起碼用到一半時間 用呢幾萬蚊可以帶比你好大滿足 甘我又覺得無咩問題"},{"pid":"f71b16a384fa4e650885bc49bd8c7ed2dc3291b8","tid":2378460,"uid":60042,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:26:23.000Z","msg":"有興趣睇下下面段片 呢條友既片我係佢身上學到唔小野<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Cp4y1U7fp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2FBV1Cp4y1U7fp&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=26c261d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Cp4y1U7fp</a><br />\n大陸網 普通話注意"},{"pid":"e812fd6c96b5bbb9d9ad8b1b652379bd1753b8df","tid":2378460,"uid":10889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:33:07.000Z","msg":"買唔買都係會冇錢 咁不如買啲心頭好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26cbd7cd4e5345894f1aac91de681c8b2470c9e9","tid":2378460,"uid":347580,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"其實睇入收入幾多啦<br />\n如果搵廿萬一個月 咁買幾萬蚊個袋<br />\n唔會影響生活咪冇問題<br />\n但如果一個袋 係你幾個月人工<br />\n就要諗一諗 set個銀碼響非必要開支上面<br />\n例如一個月3000買無謂野<br />\n過左 就唔買 一係儲起個3000 <br />\n到儲到幾萬 個陣仲想買先買"},{"pid":"eb11707bfb2fc1eb84489ce417d11264dabfcfb3","tid":2378460,"uid":41922,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:49:37.000Z","msg":"啲錢只係變左你想要嘅形狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\